      <h2>Brand Identity</h2>

      <p>The publication name is always written as <strong>The Freethinking Times</strong> — capitalised, no abbreviation. The icon is a serif "F" on a dark square. The pansy flower — a historical symbol of freethought (from the French <em>pens&eacute;e</em>, meaning "thought") — is the publication's mascot and will replace the favicon in a future update.</p>

      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-4);padding:var(--space-6);background:var(--color-bg-alt);border:1px solid var(--color-rule);margin:var(--space-6) 0;">
